text: I planted a seed. Finally grow fruits. Today is a great day. Pick off the star for you. Pick off the moon for you.
Let it rise for you every day. Become candles burning myself.
Just light you up, hey! Give you my everything. As long as you enjoy, ha!
You let my every tomorrow become meaningful, hey! Life with loving you forever, never abandon!
You are my little little apple. How much love you, still no enough.
Red smile warms my heart. Light my life's fire, fire, fire, fire, fire.
You are my little little apple. Like the most beautiful clouds in the sky.
Spring comes again. Flowers are in full bloom on mountain slope. Planted hope will reap.
Never dislike you. Like your everything. With you, everyday is fresh. With you, sunshine is more brilliant.
With you, there is no dark night. You're white clouds, I'm the blue sky.
In the spring, with you, walk among the flowers. In the summer night, with you watch winking stars together.
In the autumn dusk, with you, wander in golden wheat fields. In the winter, snowflakes flutter, with you , so warmer.
